AIR FREIGHT CHAUFFEURS, HANDLERS, WAREHOUSEMEN,
ALLIED WORKERS, MISCELLANEOUS, PRODUCTION AND INDUSTRIAL EMPLOYEES
AFFILIATED WITH THE INTERNATIONAL BROTHERHOOD OF TEAMSTERS






Welcome to the International Brotherhood of TeamstersLocal Union No. 295

You are part of a proud tradition in the labor movement. For almost 100 years, the Teamsters Union has been a leader in setting the standard for higher wages, better benefits and improved working conditions for workers throughout the United States and Canada. Local 295 has been part of that tradition for 50 of those 100 years serving the people in the Tri-State area.
This Union is committed to negotiating the best collective bargaining agreements and providing the strongest day-to-day representation for all. Everyone benefits from the Teamsters Union when the members unite to achieve common goals. We encourage you to become an informed and active member and work with us to bring dignity, justice and fairness to the workplace.
